  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为HealthTech实验室分析系统画一个架构图。核心有三个模块：HIPAA合规的数据保险库、患者记录系统，还有诊断引擎。这三个都要放在一个ROS2的子图里。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ROS2",
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，ROS2子图命名为HealthTech_LabAnalyzer。C1是HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault，C2是HealthTech_PatientRecords，C3是HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine。确认一下，这三个都是ROS2内部的节点吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ROS2",
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，都是ROS2节点。另外还需要一个独立的硬件接口层，叫HWI子图，里面放SI节点，也就是EMR同步模块。这个SI负责桥接ROS2和底层硬件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HWI",
        "SI"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，HWI子图命名为HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault，SI节点是HealthTech_EMR_Sync。已经画好了。接下来硬件部分怎么安排？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HWI",
        "SI"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "硬件层单独放一个Hardware子图，里面三个模块M1、M2、M3。M1对应HIPAA保险库的硬件存储，M2是实验室分析仪本体，M3是诊断引擎的硬件加速单元。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Hardware",
        "M1",
        "M2",
        "M3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Hardware子图命名为HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine。M1是HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault，M2是HealthTech_LabAnalyzer，M3是HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine。这里命名有点容易混淆，M1和C1都叫HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault，但一个是硬件一个是软件层，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Hardware",
        "M1",
        "M2",
        "M3",
        "C1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，故意这样设计的，表示软硬件对应关系。现在画连接关系：C1、C2、C3都要单向指向SI，表示数据流向EMR同步模块。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C3",
        "SI"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "C1到SI、C2到SI、C3到SI的单向连接已添加。那SI到硬件层呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C3",
        "SI"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "SI和M1、M2、M3之间是双向通信，用双向箭头。因为EMR同步既要下发配置到硬件，也要读取硬件状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SI",
        "M1",
        "M2",
        "M3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "SI和M1、M2、M3的双向连接已完成。整体结构看起来是：ROS2子图三个节点都指向HWI的SI，然后SI再双向连接Hardware的三个模块。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SI",
        "M1",
        "M2",
        "M3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，我刚才说HWI子图命名是HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault，这个不对。HWI应该叫HealthTech_HardwareInterface，不是HIPAA_Vault。HIPAA_Vault是C1和M1的名字。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HWI"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "收到，修正HWI子图名称为HealthTech_HardwareInterface。但代码里显示HWI子图名还是HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault，我需要再确认——",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HWI"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "抱歉我搞混了。看最终代码，HWI子图名确实是HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault，SI节点在里面。Hardware子图才是HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine。保持代码里的命名，不用改。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HWI",
        "Hardware",
        "SI"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认，HWI子图名为HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault，包含SI节点。Hardware子图名为HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine，包含M1、M2、M3。这样命名虽然有点反直觉，但按您的要求保持。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HWI",
        "Hardware",
        "SI",
        "M1",
        "M2",
        "M3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "再检查一下连接：C1、C2、C3到SI是单向箭头，SI到M1、M2、M3是双向箭头。这样体现数据从ROS2流向同步层，再和硬件双向交互。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C3",
        "SI",
        "M1",
        "M2",
        "M3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认，C1-SI、C2-SI、C3-SI是单向，SI-M1、SI-M2、SI-M3是双向。所有连接都已正确标注。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C3",
        "SI",
        "M1",
        "M2",
        "M3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "M2的命名是HealthTech_LabAnalyzer，这和ROS2子图名HealthTech_LabAnalyzer重复了，没问题吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "M2",
        "ROS2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "Mermaid中子图和节点可以有相同标签，内部ID不同。M2是节点ID，显示文本是HealthTech_LabAnalyzer，ROS2子图显示文本也是HealthTech_LabAnalyzer，技术上可行。",
